## Examples

```html
<!-- Semantic HTML -->
<nav><header><main><footer><article><section>

<!-- Alt text -->
<img src="logo.png" alt="Company Logo">

<!-- ARIA labels -->
<button aria-label="Close dialog">×</button>

<!-- Form labels -->
<label for="email">Email</label>
<input id="email" type="email">

<!-- Keyboard navigation -->
<button tabindex="0">Clickable</button>
```

